    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept vehicle in good overall condition. The exterior presents nicely with normal light wear for its age, and the interior is clean and comfortable with typical signs of use but nothing excessive. It appears to have been maintained and should make a solid daily driver for someone looking for a dependable, presentable car without paying mint-condition money. Buyers can expect a sound used vehicle that shows honest age-appropriate wear rather than a perfect showroom example.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Mint-condition vehicle that shows exceptionally well inside and out. The exterior is very clean with a glossy finish, straight body panels, and no notable cosmetic issues, and the interior is equally well-kept with minimal to no visible wear. It has clearly been carefully maintained and should appeal to buyers looking for a very clean, well-preserved example. Expect a vehicle that feels close to showroom quality and is ready to enjoy.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a value-focused buyer who wants practical daily use without a big upfront cost. A solid opportunity for someone seeking inexpensive transportation, a backup vehicle, or a project with potential.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, moves, and could make a handy runabout, first project, or parts donor depending on what you need. Priced honestly for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re after a cheap car with potential, this is worth a look.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Clean, honest project-grade driver with strong mechanical character and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain starts up willingly, pulls through the rev range, and the chassis remains straightforward and predictable on the road. Not a showpiece, but a solid platform for someone who wants an affordable daily, weekend fixer, or practical budget commuter with proven hardware and easy service access. Ideal for a buyer who values mechanical simplicity, low-cost ownership, and the chance to tidy it up over time.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Not pretty, but dependable enough for work, project, or cheap wheels. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with tons of personality, this car has the kind of road-worn charm that makes it perfect for someone who sees possibility where others see patina. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership, whether you want a budget-friendly runabout, a project with character, or a practical set of wheels with plenty of life stories already built in. The body and cabin show their age, but that seasoned look only adds to its scrappy appeal. If you want something inexpensive, honest, and full of potential, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation with solid value for the price. This vehicle is being offered in as-is condition and is well-suited for a buyer looking for a budget-conscious daily driver, a backup vehicle, or a practical project. A great opportunity to get behind the wheel at an accessible price point.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
